# ==============================================================
# VatesVMS Evaluate-STIG — Git Ignore Rules
#
# What IS tracked (custom work):
#   .Mods_by_Kismet/              — integration guide, docs, test scripts
#   Evaluate-STIG/Modules/Scan-XCP-ng_*/   — custom XCP-ng check modules
#   Evaluate-STIG/Modules/Scan-XO_*/       — custom Xen Orchestra check modules
#   Evaluate-STIG/xml/STIGList.xml         — modified (custom STIG entries added)
#   Evaluate-STIG/xml/FileList.xml         — modified (custom module entries added)
#   Evaluate-STIG/AnswerFiles/XCP-ng_*.xml — custom XCP-ng answer files
#   Evaluate-STIG/AnswerFiles/XO_*.xml     — custom XO answer files
#   README.md                              — project overview (root)
#
# What is NOT tracked (NAVSEA Evaluate-STIG framework):
#   All other Evaluate-STIG files/folders — not for redistribution
#   Evaluate-STIG/StigContent/            — DISA benchmark files (separate license)
#   Evaluate-STIG/Modules/Master_Functions/ — framework core (mods documented in
#                                             .Mods_by_Kismet/Docs/MODIFICATIONS.md)
#
# To use this repo: clone it, then download and integrate the NAVSEA
# Evaluate-STIG framework following .Mods_by_Kismet/README.md.
# ==============================================================


